      "[azure] az resolved: /usr/bin/az (reason=ranked selection)\n",
      "[azure] az version: azure-cli                         2.78.0 *\n",
      "[azure] Active subscription: d334f2cd-3efd-494e-9fd3-2470b1a13e4c\n",
