    "        print(\"-\" * 80)\n",
    "        print(\"\"\"\n",
    "1. REPOSITORY HEALTH:\n",
    "   The repository shows strong community engagement with high star count\n",
    "   and active development (recent commits). The open issues indicate an\n",
    "   active user base providing feedback.\n",
